{"tid":2112403,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（TG Group）中學學術解答群組","createTime":"2020-07-17T09:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T10:10:37.000Z","uid":64673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"05884a925d6bed046d01de5c83d825b6de44f2fa","tid":2112403,"uid":64673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"由於疫情關係，相信好多中學同學都未能夠跟上學校進度<br />\n因此，我同我嘅團隊開左tg group為各同學解答學術疑難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n群組分為三個<br />\nS1-S3 全科學術解答<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J-ZofhtOXOT_ydDoDWWWuw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ-ZofhtOXOT_ydDoDWWWuw&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=e2128982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J-ZofhtOXOT_ydDoDWWWuw</a><br />\nS4-S6 英文學術解答數學<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J-Zofhhgt18Y5jqVx8RjKA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ-Zofhhgt18Y5jqVx8RjKA&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=5f3b514a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J-Zofhhgt18Y5jqVx8RjKA</a><br />\nS4-S6 數學學術解答<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J-ZofkVrfp_3JuFF6IB_OQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ-ZofkVrfp_3JuFF6IB_OQ&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=33310443\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J-ZofkVrfp_3JuFF6IB_OQ</a><br />\n<br />\n其他學科將會逐一建立群組<br />\n同學可以入返相應嘅群組<br />\n<br />\n我哋會盡力為大家解答問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎其他巴絲加入討論及交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5a3b8170255e61cabe5c54002824e0e140e774","tid":2112403,"uid":187991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"咁好"}]}